Aviva Group Holdings Limited: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 8:09 AM ET
Insurance

Company Overview of Aviva Group Holdings Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Aviva Group Holdings Limited is a holding company. The company, through its subsidiaries, offers life, health, general, and casualty insurance services. The company was formerly known as Norwich Union Holdings Limited and changed its name to Aviva Group Holdings Limited in September, 2006. The company was incorporated in 1981 and is based in London, United Kingdom. Aviva Group Holdings Limited operates as a subsidiary of Aviva plc.


St Helen's1 UndershaftLondon,  EC3P 3DQUnited KingdomFounded in 1981



Phone: 44 2072 832 000

Fax: 44 1603 683 659








